{"tid":587872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投廢票！不要遲投票、不要投白票、不要唔投票、不要含撚投票！","createTime":"2018-03-10T18:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:01:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":48,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8f815a810a1b8bab970bf42601ed441bbf7a55b8","tid":587872,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"唔好投白票！<br />\n港共殖民政府操控既選舉, 白票有可能被人做手腳, <br />\n唔知選舉事務處班殖民狗仆街會唔會幫你投<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔投票！<br />\n你唔去投, 就可能會有不明人士盜用你既身份, 去投左你個票<br />\n以往曾發生多次, 有市民去票站, 發覺已經有人用左自己既身份投左, 自己無得投<br />\n可以GOOGLE返以前新聞<br />\n所以唔好遲投票<br />\n<br />\n投廢票, 可以盡情發揮創意<br />\n<br />\n選特首既權貴, 係咁樣投廢票既：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170326/640_865ebc99c7af500427a284f939dda2c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170326%2F640_865ebc99c7af500427a284f939dda2c8.jpg&h=45fec937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170326/640_2037f9aeca28186822383983ba227e57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170326%2F640_2037f9aeca28186822383983ba227e57.jpg&h=481ece1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後, 當然係唔好再含撚投票<br />\n<br />\n我就由出世至今, 做左咁多年人, 都無試過含撚投票"},{"pid":"687de8925095dae1fd98d6eace8e49a0fbee8cb1","tid":587872,"uid":79563,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:17:09.000Z","msg":"我投得最開心既一次<br />\n<br />\n係投梁天琦"},{"pid":"9180fe0d304ad0fdaf28599dd5664dbe222d6bc2","tid":587872,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:36:41.000Z","msg":"有小小鬼"},{"pid":"ec4edbafda08236f14cf5dd85454b748a3276e5e","tid":587872,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:52:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"185b9b12eaeb6335dfab444d9852e3107c0ff7e1","tid":587872,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:58:50.000Z","msg":"冇人投得落手"},{"pid":"2fd41942cf9adc8a5706a03d469c778e2d6e0e63","tid":587872,"uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"係西方文明國家, 如果選舉被操控, 呼籲杯葛選舉根本係常識, 係常事黎<br />\n<br />\n唔信你自己GOOGLE下新聞「杯葛選舉」<br />\n<br />\n係港豬政治智商低下, 民智未開, 先會有「含撚投票」呢件事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59174afe02d7146123d184fd531a713fda3fec2","tid":587872,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"已投梁天埼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46704ee3e6aea0f7605e332d9bebf6259dbc9e42","tid":587872,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae3e1f4043e86b5ac9f223155afda829a971903","tid":587872,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"有無得點票個陣show出嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd1524c56b79841416a16a98d2330f4b64afc8e","tid":587872,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f26c2a558dbea87246a6c4c24d832bd373aef55","tid":587872,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e59174afe02d7146123d184fd531a713fda3fec2","tid":587872,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"已投梁天埼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s